{"pageProps":{"title":"double二进制布局","date":"2020-08-26 14:20","author":[{"name":"mq","link":""}],"html":"<h1>double二进制布局</h1>\n<h2>IEEE754</h2>\n<pre><code>+-+-----------+----------------------------------------------------+\n|s| exp(11bit)|                     mantissa(52bit)                |\n+-+-----------+----------------------------------------------------+\n</code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>exp存的移码（真实值+1023)</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>mantissa二进制小数去掉最高位的非零：1.xxxxxxxx(2) 只保留 x 的部分</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>s是符号位</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>真实值 = $ {s} \\cdot 1 . {mantissa} \\cdot 2 ^ { exp - 1023 } $</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>e.g. 1.5</h3>\n<pre><code>+-+-----------+----------------------------------------------------+\n|0|01111111111|1000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000000|\n+-+-----------+----------------------------------------------------+\n|+|   1023    |                  2251799813685248                  |\n+-+-----------+----------------------------------------------------+\n</code></pre>\n<h3>e.g. 最大奇数</h3>\n<pre><code>+-+-----------+----------------------------------------------------+\n|0|10000110011|1111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111111|\n+-+-----------+----------------------------------------------------+\n</code></pre>\n"},"__N_SSG":true}